# Emails granted elevated roles at account setup (setupAccountHandle).
# Comma-separated. Copy to functions/.env and fill in - the functions build FAILS
# while either key is missing, empty or not a list of email addresses.
#
# ADMIN_EMAILS must register with the Google popup: that branch requires a verified
# token email and the email+password flow never verifies one. DASHBOARD_EMAILS has
# no such gate - that role grants no data access.
ADMIN_EMAILS=
DASHBOARD_EMAILS=
